description: Simple skill that reads you famous quotes from history and movies.  Just say "Alexa, ask Famous Quotes for a quote".
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask Famous Quotes to tell me quote.
Alexa, tell Famous Quotes to give me a quote.
Alexa, use Famous Quotes to tell me another quote.
name: Famous Quotes
shortDescription: Simple skill that reads you famous quotes from history and movies.
